      <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Heading1">ERASE Command</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><snippet src="__CommandInclude" inline="false"/></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Heading1">Purpose</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">Remove a file from disk.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Heading1">Syntax</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">ERASE | DELETE FILE &lt;<text styleclass="Italic">xcSourceFile</text>&gt;</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Heading1">Description</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">ERASE is the same as DELETE FILE. &#160;See DELETE FILE for a complete explanation of this command.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
